  "name": "Track Your Email Events",
  "body": "<p>Furthermore, you can see the event timeline of each email by clicking on the email record. The event timeline opens in a side panel and contains the email details along with the timeline of events.</p>\n<p><span>In Navigation, go to EMAIL, and select Events. </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png\" width=\"699\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 344px; width: 699px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao4rqEAB.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Click an email record to open the Timeline panel for the email.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"319\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png\" width=\"687\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 319px; width: 687px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao4ZVEAZ.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
